             was indicted for <rs id="t18220522-66-off358" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220522-66-off358" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220522-66-off358" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220522-66-cd359" type="crimeDate">3rd of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-66-off358 t18220522-66-cd359"></join>, one hat, value 10 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220522-66-victim621" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
                           Angelo
                        <interp inst="t18220522-66-victim621" type="surname" value="Angelo"></interp>
